{"id":340417,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/蘋果日報-鍾楚紅-艾未未-「美女與野獸」合照/","date":"2014-03-30T21:19:21Z","modified":"2014-03-30T21:19:21Z","title":"蘋果日報 | 鍾楚紅 艾未未 「美女與野獸」合照","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"鍾楚紅雖息影多年，但風采絲毫不減。資料照片\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2F%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20140331%2FLN15%2FLN15_004.jpg\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20140331/35735754_d3debef20f377ed220234b8e51abe2f8_160x160.jpg\"></a><span>鍾楚紅雖息影多年，但風采絲毫不減。資料照片</span></p>\n<p>【大陸中心╱綜合外電報導】致力維權運動的北京藝術家艾未未與女星鍾楚紅「相見歡」！熱愛藝術的鍾楚紅，日前到北京拜訪艾未未，前天艾把兩人合照po上網，有網友驚嘆鍾楚紅「還是這麼美」，還有人調侃是「美女與野獸」。</p>\n<hr>\n<hr><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"艾未未（左）與鍾楚紅日前在北京相見歡，網友調侃「美女與野獸」。翻攝網路\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2F%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20140331%2FLN15%2FLN15_005.jpg\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20140331/35735754_26a39a65306517e6ac52e01f8f50983b_160x160.jpg\"></a><span>艾未未（左）與鍾楚紅日前在北京相見歡，網友調侃「美女與野獸」。翻攝網路</span></p>\n<p>艾未未前天透過Instagram發布這張兩人在他北京自宅的合影（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FmHYYDkqD6v%2F\">instagram.com/p/mHYYDkqD6v/</a>）。「紅姑」鍾楚紅戴墨鏡、穿紅針織衫，笑容燦爛，當時中國搖滾樂手左小祖咒（本名吳紅巾）也在場。網友大讚鍾楚紅「好美」，但也有人擔心鍾楚紅與艾未未走太近，「小心被封殺」。<br />《蘋果》昨數度致電艾未未，但無法聯繫上。香港《明報》昨引述艾未未表示，鍾楚紅是「朋友私人訪問」。他說他們聊了藝術和旅行，並未談及其他，至於如何結識紅姑，艾未未不願透露。<br />56歲的艾未未是國際知名藝術家，2008年他發起調查汶川大地震死難學生名單，遭當局封殺，曾多次遭毆打、拘留。左小祖咒常透過歌曲抨擊社會不公，2012年抵抗自家遭強拆成為焦點。</p>\n<hr><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Fforum\">【蘋論陣線】：最新評論及獨立媒體每日總覽</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com/?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=mailto%3Aonlineopinions%40appledaily.com.tw%3Fsubject%3D%25A6%25B3%25B8%25DC%25ADn%25BB%25A1%25A7%25EB%25BDZ%25A1u%25A7Y%25AE%25C9%25BD%25D7%25BE%25C2%25A1v\">有話要說 投稿「即時論壇」</a></p>\n<p>onlineopinions@appledaily.com.tw</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1000,"categories":[18270,18269,18424],"tags":[19188,11945,8712]}